<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-6 text-gray-800 mt-25">
    {/* Título principal */}
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    {/* Sección: Introducción */}
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6">Abel Garcia Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
        This Privacy Policy describes how this website collects, uses, and protects your personal 
        information when you use our website and services.
    </p>

    {/* Sección: Información que recolectamos */}
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mt-6">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
        We may collect the following types of information:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-2">
        <li>
        <strong>Information you provide:</strong> This includes information you submit when registering, 
        contacting us, or using our services.
        </li>
        <li>
        <strong>Usage data:</strong> We automatically collect information about how you use our services, 
        such as the pages you visit and the features you use.
        </li>
        <li>
        <strong>Device information:</strong> We may collect information about your device, such as your 
        IP address and browser type.
        </li>
    </ul>

    {/* Sección: Uso de la información */}
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mt-6">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">We use your information to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-2">
        <li>Provide and improve our services.</li>
        <li>Personalize your experience.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about our services.</li>
        <li>Comply with legal requirements.</li>
    </ul>

    {/* Sección: Seguridad de datos */}
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mt-6">3. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized 
        access, use, or disclosure.
    </p>

    {/* Sección: Retención de datos */}
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mt-6">4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
        We retain your information only as long as necessary for the purposes described in this 
        Privacy Policy or as required by law.
    </p>

    {/* Sección: Tus derechos */}
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mt-6">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
        You have the right to access, correct, and delete your personal information. Please contact us 
        at <a href="mailto:contact@agrubio.dev" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact@agrubio.dev</a> to exercise these rights.
    </p>

    {/* Sección: Contacto */}
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mt-6">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
        If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at 
        <a href="mailto:contact@agrubio.dev" class="text-blue-600 underline"> contact@agrubio.dev</a>.
    </p>
</section>